üé≤Connect & Play

Getting new players involved in games requires a lot of explanation, and often a download is needed to start playing.

The BG platform is browser based and the games are simple, easy to understand, can be finished within 5 minutes or less, and are a lot of fun!

ü´Ç Player Limits

On the BoardGamers platform you can host lobbies with  100+ players.
